Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高文 为什么你要拒绝露卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的想法告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上面 亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚修
